        public java.lang.Object expressGene(C_Gene gL,
                           C_Gene gR)
        Takes a pair of genes from a diploid genome and express their value as the sum of the alleles stored here. This assumes the the alleles stored in these genes are Numbers.
        Specified by:
        expressGene in interface I_gene_pair_evaluator
        Parameters:
        gL - the left gene in the pair (must contain a Number allele)
        gR - the right gene in the pair (must contain a Number allele)
